name: iShares Flexible Monthly Income ETF (CAD-Hedged)
longDescription: To achieve its objective ETF investing in debt and income producing securities with a secondary objective of capital appreciation. The ETF invests primarily in one or more iShares ETFs or directly in fixed income securities. Currently, the ETF invests all or substantially all of its assets in the BlackRock Flexible Income ETF. The ETF seeks to maximize longterm income.
